  "title": "Locum Admin Assistant (School Health Screening Project / Mon - Fri  7.30am to 4 pm) #HAL",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong><br />Monday to Friday (No work during school holidays)<br />7.30am to 4 pm daily </p><p><strong>Location</strong>: Central /  North </p><p><strong>Salary: </strong>$10.5/hour (No CPF)</p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in school health screening activities</li><li>Take height and weight measurements</li><li>Conduct hearing checks</li><li>Support school health team in other assigned administrative tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Comfortable with travelling to different schools within assigned zones</li><li>Able to commit for min 6 months and longer</li><li>Tdap and MMR vaccinated </li></ul><p><br />Interested candidate, kindly send a copy of your resume to <strong>adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p><p>Adeline Lim Xin Ying [R23112000]</p><p>Email Address: adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p>",
